typo in RU locale in abbreviation for January

For additional info/opinions on abbreviations of months in Russian see: http://forum.gramota.ru/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=5411
The standardized abbreviations as some people say are: 
Jan=янв.
Feb=февр.
Apr=апр.
Aug=авг.
Sep=сент.
Oct=окт.
Nov=нояб.
Dec=дек. 
+ no abbreviations for Mar, May, Jun and Jul.
